      <p class="section-title">// ABOUT ME</p>
      <div class="about-me-content">
        <div class="about-me-logo">
          <%= image_tag "jks-signature-logo.svg", alt: "jks", class: "about-logo" %>
        </div>
        <div class="about-me-text">
          <h2 class="my-name">Joseph Kim-Suzuki</h2>
          <p class="my-subtitle">Aspiring Shopify RIR Engineer</p>
          <p>Bilingual support engineer based in Hakodate, Japan. I build tools, troubleshoot systems, and document everything — working toward Resiliency Incident Response at Shopify APAC.</p>
          <p>I learn by doing — building, breaking, and improving. SignalDesk is proof of that: a real observability platform built to mirror the work I'm targeting.</p>
          <div class="about-details">
            <span>Hakodate, Japan</span>
            <span>Started 2024</span>
            <span>English · 日本語 · 한국어 · Français</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-row">
    <div class="mission panel">
