      <h3 class="mission-headline">Resiliency Incident Response Engineer, Shopify APAC</h3>
      <p>The RIR role sits at the intersection of customer support and systems engineering. ClassPass Bugs Squad. SignalDesk. Prometheus, Grafana, Slack alerting. Deliberate reps toward one role. I don't wait for problems to surface — I go looking for them.</p>
      <div class="mission-items">
        <div class="mission-item">
          <span class="mission-check"></span>
          <div>
