            <p class="mission-item-subtitle">Investigate failures fast, minimise merchant impact, restore systems.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-item">
          <span class="mission-check"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="mission-item-title">Find root cause, not just symptoms</p>
            <p class="mission-item-subtitle">Document every step. Fix the thing that caused the thing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-item">
          <span class="mission-check"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="mission-item-title">Stay curious</p>
            <p class="mission-item-subtitle">Never satisfied with "it's working now." Always asking why it broke in the first place.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

